verbose_text: The data also suggest that Rickettsiales bacteria are likely not involved in causing WBD (type I); if Rickettsiales were involved in causing WBD as suggested previously XREF_BIBR, then we would have not expected Ampicillin which is not effective against obligate intracellular bacteria such as Rikettsia XREF_BIBR, to completely supress WBD transmission.
